n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e4ac7584eaa1e20ac539a221008f8f8e5332b33","tid":1541302,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:16:40.000Z","msg":"爭你"},{"pid":"9bfe02ca51b464884cab1c2292f34668937aa363","tid":1541302,"uid":261300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:17:35.000Z","msg":"借位推post<br />\n[膊頭有花入]大家應該調轉分析下，林鄭撤回將會係我地connect對家既最好時機<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540580</a>"},{"pid":"e4d057b6bda744ecdc7f5468d75514bd15fd0d16","tid":1541302,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"一個"},{"pid":"e6538274e3c712a0d65787142eb7cf17f08b5e3e","tid":1541302,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"來來來"},{"pid":"20faf4b3e960f27debf00e679723894b6bb0ebe6","tid":1541302,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:25:56.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"b80b